column5: Id seen alot of these before, but there were a few I hadnt so I thought Id share... Merry Xmas.

Oh TJ, thank you!  I have a funeral tomorrow for my grandmother and things have been rather 'un-Christmas like' this week.  That is the first thing I have not just smiled about, but laughed out loud at, so far in the last week!  Thank you!
seen them before but you just have to  laugh at him each time you see him....  I hear the 3 stooges based their slapstick routine on him..LOL
